headline: B. Thomas Golisano, Paychex Founder, to Step Down from Company’s Board of Directors
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., May 16, 2025--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX), an industry-leading human capital management (HCM) company, today announced that the company’s Founder, B. Thomas Golisano, has decided to step down from his role as a member of the Paychex Board of Directors effective after the Board’s July, 2025 meeting.
